ba1fd","tid":2209171,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:13:32.000Z","msg":"馬化騰早年已入股香港兩大網上討論區：「香港討論區」（香討）及「Uwants」的非控制股權，但就否認入股小米。<br />\n<br />\n香討為目前本港最受歡迎的討論網站之一，根據互聯網統計公司Alexa統計顯示，「香港討論區」及「Uwants」於香港互聯網的排名分別為14位及25位，其中「香港討論區」的註冊會員超過200萬，平均每日上網人次超過80萬。由於討論話題多涉及政治及社會層面，故長期被內地網絡封鎖。馬化騰未有進一步指入股比例，只稱不是控股股東（50%以下）。"},{"pid":"084c05cef790ff5730b103e840958d73592a5a55","tid":2209171,"uid":34789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:16:51.000Z","msg":"仲有人上香討u汪嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934b0dfd3ee60801097ab7b46645cdd2a41a50a7","tid":2209171,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:23:41.000Z","msg":"埋伏於香討的連登pr<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沒有連登狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba9836aa3551a3fb6674aa826ce9063d8023249","tid":2209171,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"28b539cd934c7635a32aa2eb2e816750179219c3","tid":2209171,"uid":42246,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T12:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/geJkHwe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgeJkHwe.jpg&h=8777f106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又直接偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6t7xyCV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6t7xyCV.png&h=5b20a23a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高登潮文都拎來討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/